Github Content Manager
======================

Installation Javascript
-----------------------

Download the [Javascript SDK](sdk/gcm.js)

    <script type="text/javascript" src="/path/to/gcm.js"></script>

Installation Node.js
--------------------

Install `gcm` package using `npm`

    npm install gcm
